Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回答这么快就是不好的表现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you say it that fast, it kind of implies you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 再问我一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing, Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想 这事很复杂 毕竟感觉这东西...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a moment. It's really complicated 'cause, you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我一直被困在这里 自从...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on, man, I've been stuck in here since...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我想他 他对我来说很重要 我既伤心又难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I miss him. He meant a lot to me. So, yeah. Upset and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好奇的是跨年夜的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was actually wondering about New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个在舞会上吵架了 那是你最后一次和他说话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two got into it at the dance. Was that the last time you spoke to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家时 他站在门廊上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I got home, he was on the porch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我该跟他聊聊的 但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should've talked to him, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你后悔吗  - 当然后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you regret that? - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你和一个人最后相处的时光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your final moment with someone 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不能定义你们整体的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}doesn't define your whole time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,道理是这个道理 但事实往往如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It shouldn't, but it often does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在我和乔尔相处的最后时光里 他曾说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my last moment with Joel, he said he
