Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他干什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it that he said that he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,问题就在这儿 他的话前后不搭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's the thing. It didn't really make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说“我救了她”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said, "I saved her."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他救过我很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved me a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对 换我也会这么想 但那不算“对不起”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I would think so. But that's not wronging someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我没觉得他对不起我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't feel wronged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他说的是什么 真希望我能放过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, I wish I could have let him off the hook for whatever it was he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只能放过自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I'll have to let myself off the hook for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you really are doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果人人都像你这么健康 我还怎么换取大麻和酒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if everyone were as healthy as you, what would I do for weed and booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 这镇上还有很多操蛋的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't worry, Gail, there's still a lot of fucked up people in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对 但你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. But not you, though.
