Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(乔尔 谢谢你做的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我去医院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么时候让你出院的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When'd they let you out?
