Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让我见盖尔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They made me talk to Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never said--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你来看了我那么多次 我早该说谢谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have said thank you for all those times you came to visit.
