Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 也许不会那么频繁 - 是啊 可能不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, maybe not as often. - Yeah, no, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了饼干给你吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made you cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just 'cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算是一份和解礼吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要让你生气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm about to make you angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾问过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you asked me 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那天的事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我没听到任何有用的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I didn't learn anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我没说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们大部分人的名字 也知道他们是哪里来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know most of their names, and I know where they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, just listen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生叫我不要让你太激动 - 我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The doctors told me not to upset you. - I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我一旦说出他们在哪 你会拔掉输液管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I knew that if I told you where they were, you'd just start pulling your tubes out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,爬也要爬过去找他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and crawling on your hands and knees to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你浪费了我们的时间 你让他们逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cost us time. You let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几个星期以来 这镇上一片狼藉 到处都是葬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this town was wreckage and funerals for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会去追杀任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody was gonna go after anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我突然想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then it occurred to me, if you wanna find someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想找一个人 而你只知道对方最终的目的地...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the only thing you know about them is where they're gonna end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如让对方先到了再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe let them get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I loved him too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们先说名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's start with names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个黑发男叫曼尼 另一个男的叫欧文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dark-haired guy was Manny. The other guy was Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,黑发女孩和光头女孩里有一个叫诺拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl with the dark hair and the bald one, one of them's named Nora. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不确定是哪个 - 那个扎辫子的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not sure which. - The girl with the braid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来自什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一个背包上看到了一块布章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw a patch on a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,黄色三角 有个狼头...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yellow triangle, wolf's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还有三个字母 WLF\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the letters W-L-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得尤金给我讲过 他还在火萤时的一个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then, I remembered a story Eugene told me from back when he was a Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有些地区性小团体 都想对抗联邦救灾局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that there were these small regional groups in the West all trying to fight FEDRA,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还说他们没有联合起来真够蠢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how stupid it was that they didn't just join together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个团体就是华盛顿解放阵线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of those groups was the Washington Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来自西雅图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WLF 狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}W-L-F. Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一群傻逼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他有说这个团体有多小吗  - 没说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did he say how small they were? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 既然从那以后没人提过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But seeing as how no one's ever mentioned them since,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜应该是我们能应付的小团体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing small enough for us to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谁知道这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我没打算在告诉你之前告诉任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't gonna tell anyone before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我得考虑一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑什么 我们去干掉那些家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think about what? Let's fucking get these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 事情没那么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie, it ain't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小镇还在恢复中 你也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The town is still recovering. So are you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们明白你的出发点 - 不 我们不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We get where you're coming from-- - No, we don't get where you're coming from. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 如果死的人是你 乔尔早在天亮前就赶往西雅图了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get where you're coming from. If it had been you, Joel would be halfway to Seattle before the sun came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么做一定是为了救我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd be halfway to Seattle to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可我们现在有伤亡 还不能走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when we lost people, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,换他也会崩溃的 他会把一切责任揽到自己身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would just break him like it was his fault. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过很多次了 别以为我不了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw that time and time again. And don't talk to me like I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不是说你不该去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I'm not sayin' you shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然要组队 就得组一支像样的队伍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we're gonna put a posse together, we gotta do it right, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉玛丽亚 没错 必须告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means taking it to Maria. Yes, it's fuckin' necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她会召开议会 通知全镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gonna want a council meeting, open it up to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,每个想发声的人都能发声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone who wants to get heard gets heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你会支持我们的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you'll back us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再有事瞒着我 就去最累的岗位上待一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you hold out information on me again, you got rendering detail for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 艾莉...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把死者埋在镇南十英里的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We buried our dead ten miles south of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅图的时候再去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we're on our way to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(普吉特步道 植物园 西雅图步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没人跟来 很安全 继续前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"No one following. All clear. Keep moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们重新安顿好 我们会教你吹口哨的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once we get resettled, I'll teach you to whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不能告诉我目的地是哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why can't you tell me where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经说了我们要去的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've told you the reason we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但她为什么不能保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, but why can't she just keep us safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Prophet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她十年前就死了 康斯坦丝 我可不会指望她帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been dead ten years, Constance. I wouldn't count on her to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但艾斯拉说先知是永生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Ezra said the Prophet is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从某种角度看没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she is, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但先知不是魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A prophet isn't magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到别人看不到的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}people that see truths hidden from others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,并且不计代价分享真相的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and share that truth, no matter what the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的先知也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it was with our Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是这样让她的精神永存的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how we keep her spirit alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,遵循她的话语 服从她的教诲 同时保护自己的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow her words, we obey her teachings, but we keep ourselves safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那能给我一把锤子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, can I have a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你觉得更安全了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, you feel safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 我们现在给你的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand, what we're giving you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,会比锤子给你更多的安全感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will keep you far, far safer than a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是出离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,出离家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,出离战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,找掩护 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take cover! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是恶魔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 注意旋转 再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alright. Good, but rotate. More.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在换右边 只打右边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the right side. Just the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这边伤害更大 - 我注意到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, man, that side hurts more. - I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用力点 坚持住 最后五拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harder. Harder! Let's go! Last five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 今天到此为止 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There it is, okay. Done for the day. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一个无所事事三个月的人能做成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, for someone who sat on their ass for three months, 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得很惊喜 - 是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm pleasantly surprised. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,平时做俯卧撑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Push-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对 还在他们不注意时卷腹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and crunches when they weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了 再过几周 你就能恢复原来的状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that'll do it. A few more weeks, and you'll be right back to where you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也就是你该有的水平的八成 - 随便了 去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Which is 80% of where you should have been. - Whatever. Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你加入议会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I heard you're on the council now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你肯定知道接下来的会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you know about the meeting coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know about the meeting coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我能指望你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讨论即将开始的投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't discuss upcoming votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞什么 是我啊 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seriously? It's me. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 当时你也在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dude, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这我也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,听完大家的意见 议会才能作决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The council won't make up their mind until we hear people speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我给你一点建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, here's a little advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的想法整理清楚 写下来 明天念给大家听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Organize your thoughts, write them down, and then read 'em out loud tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道了 因为我很蠢 - 因为你愤怒 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, yeah, 'cause I'm stupid. - 'Cause you're angry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会投票给愤怒的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And no one's gonna vote for angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...所以我一直说我们要多投资火鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I keep saying we need to invest more in turkeys 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,少投资鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and less in chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这就要说回我之前对玉米的看法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that brings me back to my earlier point about corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人听我这么说过 玉米不是最容易种植的作物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Corn, some of you have heard me say, is not the easiest crop to grow, 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但它是生长最快的作物之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it is among the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以绘一张图 把收成时间和所需资源以及难易度...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can plot a graph that shows ease and resources versus time to harvest and get a li--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特 抱歉打断你 不要偏题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scott, I'm sorry, but we gotta keep you on target here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是公开会议 章程上说...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's an open meeting. The bylaws say that--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们应该回到 大家原本要讨论的议程上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should stick to what everyone else came here to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我对西雅图的事没意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really have an opinion on the Seattle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特说完了 接下来是瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, that was Scott. Next is Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见 大声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能帮我抱着他吗  - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you take him, please? - Yeah. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.77,0:24:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said that Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但他并非唯一一个重要的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he wasn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我失去了我妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost my sister that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很多人都埋葬了家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of people in here buried family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们要派去16个顶尖成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, you wanna send, what, you're saying 16 of our best?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.57,0:25:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不在的时候 如果掠夺者来了 谁去墙上抵御他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, while they're gone, who's gonna be on the wall if Raiders come?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,墙还没修好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wall that's barely mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且谁也不能保证 那16个人都能回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And none of you up there can promise us that all 16 will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.50,0:25:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我同情你们 汤米和艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, my heart is with you, Tommy and Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们伤亡惨重 现在出击太早了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are too hurt, and it is too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.13,0:25:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位是卡莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next is Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.60,0:25:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我长话短说 毕竟这是个简单的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be quick. 'Cause this one's simple to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来我们这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People came 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了乔尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and killed Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.90,0:25:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不想复仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, why wouldn't we wanna take our vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们不该那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, because we're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.74,0:25:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宽恕他人 方能被人宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive and be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.12,0:25:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放下怨恨和仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No grudges. No revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.25,0:25:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不是基督徒 可我一直觉得这么做很明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not even a Christian. I've always seen the wisdom in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我们与掠夺者和杀人犯 不同的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what separates us from the Raiders and the murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.09,0:26:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们懂得仁慈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our capacity for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些混蛋不配得到我们的仁慈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those sons of bitches don't deserve our mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.52,0:26:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不配 所以才叫仁慈啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, of course they don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的屁话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what makes it mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.23,0:26:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能这么说 也不是什么好东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, to hell with that. And to hell with you for saying it, Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赛斯 坐下 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seth, sit down. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.36,0:26:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不在发言名单上 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're not on the list. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are we all talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.61,0:26:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦 太不公平了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.07,0:26:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要原谅每一个 骑在我们头上拉屎的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, we gotta forgive everybody when they show up and piss in our eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们闯进了我们家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They came into our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抓走了我们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.04,0:26:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My God, 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.25,0:26:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有人射杀了你们的兄弟 你们还想把门锁拆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}somebody shoots your brother, you wanna take the locks off your doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,幼稚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些白痴 他们还会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You idiots, they'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.55,0:26:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们没让他们付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll come back because we didn't make 'em pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等他们回来时 一定带着嘲笑的嘴脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when they come back, they'll be laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们都活该\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you'll all deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.52,0:26:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bunch of 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.23,0:26:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}goddamn victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(斯考特 瑞秋 卡莱尔 艾莉)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.35,0:27:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“我通常不会准备发言稿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I normally don't write things down
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“因为我向来有话直说 不假思索”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I normally don't think before I talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“这让我惹上了不少麻烦”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which has gotten me in trouble before, a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“让我付出了无法挽回的代价”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's cost me in ways that sometimes couldn't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我这次输不起 因为我知道我的要求很过分”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't afford that right now, because I know what I'm asking is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.24,0:27:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要我们在最糟的时机”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm asking us to risk more people and resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.29,0:27:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“拿更多的人力和资源去冒险”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.37,0:27:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“我想告诉大家 我想要的并非复仇”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want everyone to know, it's not because I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.46,0:27:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“真的 这跟复仇无关”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not. It's not about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.92,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要的是 你们过去给予他人的东西”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want is what you used to give people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.68,0:28:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要正义”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.55,0:28:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,“因为除此之外 就只剩沉默与放弃了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it's either that, or we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.14,0:28:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“而外面的人 也只会默默地放弃我们”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what everyone else out there is going to do for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果我或你们遭遇不幸”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. A whole world of people who won't lift a finger
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.31,0:28:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“全世界没有人愿意动一动手指”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if something bad happens to me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.69,0:28:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们有专门的词称呼这种人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a word for these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“那就是‘陌生人’”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're called strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“我觉得我们之间不是陌生人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't think that we're strangers to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“我得知道我能依靠你们”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want to know that I can count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“我发誓 如果有人伤害你们或你们爱的人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I swear, if someone hurts any of you or the people you love, 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“你们也可以依靠我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.63,0:28:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“这才是我们的凝聚力”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what holds all this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.25,0:28:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是聚餐 也不是跨年舞会”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not potluck dinners or New Year's Eve dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.17,0:28:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“更不是一堵墙 因为那堵墙已经被撞破了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Definitely not a wall, because that thing got busted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.14,0:28:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“而杰克逊依然挺立”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Jackson is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会接受议会的一切决议”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll accept whatever the council decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我拜托你们”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am asking you, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.81,0:28:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“不惜一切代价伸张正义”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do what it takes to see that justice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是为了我”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.36,0:29:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“甚至不是为了乔尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even for Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“我拜托你们为我们大家这么做”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am asking you, please, do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.79,0:29:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.38,0:29:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,议会将就派遣16名成员前往西雅图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The council will now vote on the proposal to send a party of 16 citizens to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找并处决杀害乔尔之人的提案 进行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to find the people who killed Joel and execute them.
