Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.28,0:31:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 九号球员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go, nine. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 盯紧球  - 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grab the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好样的 九号  - 加油 罗德尼 冲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attaboy, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死 - 他没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.88,0:31:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你是球迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know you were a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我当年可买过老虎队的季票呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell, yeah! I had Tigers season tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这其实跟2003年的球队差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This actually isn't that far off from the '03 squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.51,0:31:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝啤酒吗 我跟马歇尔拿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want a beer? I get them from Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开会时 我在人群中看到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spotted you in the crowd at the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.58,0:31:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我心想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.95,0:32:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“她过去几周可能特别忙”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she's probably been extra busy these last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.37,0:32:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太残忍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都该去看心理医生 消化发生的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm supposed to see a shrink myself, you know, to process it all, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.13,0:32:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可这里没有别人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你怎么办  - 我是个酒鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, what do you do, then? - Oh, well, I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.26,0:32:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我尽可能地多抽大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I smoke as much weed as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一场大灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, complete fuckin' disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.27,0:32:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但你来找我不是因为担心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're not here 'cause you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,两人出局了 各位 加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two outs, guys, two outs. Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.65,0:32:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到别人看不到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see things that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心她会做傻事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm nervous she's gonna do somethin' stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 你不相信她的发言  - 你相信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What, you didn't believe her speech? - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不信 她是个骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Course not. She's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,撒谎的人不一定是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a difference between lyin' and being a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.75,0:32:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 她就是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I know. And that one? Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能只跟一个人说过实话 而他已经...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was maybe one person she told the truth to, and he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们可以在这一点上各持己见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we can agree to disagree about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:33:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是你很害怕 那我们谈谈吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What matters is you're afraid. So, let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不收钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.19,0:33:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想看她步乔尔的后尘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want her to go down the same paths that Joel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他满口的正当理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comin' up with justifications and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,其实只是在宣泄而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All he was really doin' was lashin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她的行为可能是跟他学的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you think she might have learned that behavior from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.54,0:33:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其实后天教养的作用微乎其微 其余的都是天性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turns out nurture can only do this much. The rest is nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她走上某条路 那也不是乔尔教她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she's on a path, it's not one that Joel put her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们一开始就是并肩而行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think they were walking side by side from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.93,0:33:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tommy, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她归你管了 你想帮她避开麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You inherited her, and you wanna keep her out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.23,0:33:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作为从业40年的心理医生 我劝你一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it from a psychotherapist of 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.94,0:33:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people just...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:33:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人无法拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people just can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.27,0:34:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁  - 迪娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who is it? - Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.86,0:34:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't think that is where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.37,0:34:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.84,0:35:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别劝我放弃 - 你以为我是来劝你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please don't try and talk me out of this. - You think that's why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.89,0:35:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说说你的计划吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅图杀死艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Seattle and kill Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,路线呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What route?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.94,0:35:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,西北方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面都是枪吗 有没有医疗用品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And is that all guns, or do you have medical supplies in there? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.99,0:35:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好别在你规划好的西北路线上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, better not land weird on an ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.58,0:35:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,崴了脚或发高烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or get a fever on your well-charted path "northwest."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,远离高速 避开城市或聚落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay off the highways. Steer clear of cities or settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.63,0:35:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,第一阶段是穿越国家森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First stage is through the national forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出来后 我们沿蛇河峡谷前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once we're out, we follow the Snake River Canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.01,0:35:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后穿越斯诺夸尔米山口 - 斯诺夸尔米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- then break off through the Snoqualmie Pass. - Snoqualmie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.98,0:35:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对 斯诺夸尔米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Snoqualmie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从东边接近西雅图 然后根据情况重新做评估\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approach Seattle from the east, then reassess based on what we find.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带好粮食 轻装上路 但要聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Provisions. Travel light, but smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.65,0:36:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拿厚外套当床垫 拿夹克当被子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winter coats for beds, jackets for blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.70,0:36:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,急救箱 电池和防熊喷雾都带上 你要带什么手枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First aid kits, batteries, bear spray. Now, handguns. What are you bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.16,0:36:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是乔尔的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that Joel's?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.37,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算用这个杀死她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, that's what you're gonna kill her with?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.29,0:36:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 那就留到那时候再用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fuckin' right. - Then, save it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它的速度很慢 后坐力特别强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's slow and kicks like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 你想轰掉你的屁股\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? Shoot your damn ass off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.63,0:36:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人这么劝过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每人起码得有一百发子弹 加上五十发步枪子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll want at least 100 shells apiece, plus 50 rifle rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.93,0:36:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想带什么长枪都可以 只要有瞄准镜就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring any long gun you want, as long as it's scoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.43,0:36:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,氯片 平底锅 还有帮闪闪保持干燥的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chlorine tablets, a pan, and something to keep Shimmer dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.31,0:36:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只带闪闪吗  - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just Shimmer? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们共骑一匹马 减少资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We share a horse. Fewer resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.81,0:36:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其他东西都跟你想的一样 除了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything else is what you'd figure, except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,靴子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这双匡威 也尊重你一贯的风格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love the Converse. Respect your consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.45,0:36:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能穿帆布鞋横穿荒野\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're not crossing open country in fuckin' Chucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.66,0:36:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我那么做过 - 不能穿帆布鞋 有问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've done it before. - No Chucks. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.04,0:36:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个 我们怎么弄到那么多东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, one. How the fuck are we gonna get all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.66,0:36:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你不会告诉杰西了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. No, don't tell me you told Jesse, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.71,0:36:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怀俄明队长 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain Wyoming? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢他 但他是个死守规矩的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love the man, but he's a little uptight about rules and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.84,0:37:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把你要带的衣服都穿上 口袋里装满子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wear all the clothes you're gonna bring, fill your pockets with ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.93,0:37:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其他东西必须装进枪套或背包里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything else needs to fit inside a holster or your backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.22,0:37:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凌晨三点在原来的东门见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll meet by the old east gate, 3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.89,0:37:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨三点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你可以直接问我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you could have just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.45,0:37:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I actually didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这把枪更好 跟我换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's better. Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么把它弄出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.43,0:38:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,珍宁在马厩值夜班 她理解我们想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jeanine's night watch at the stables. She's sympathetic to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Our cause"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.06,0:38:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你在议会上说“我们”的 不是我说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the one that gave the "us" speech, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.61,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,马鞍袋里都是我偷藏的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saddlebags are filled with stuff I had squirreled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.40,0:38:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃两周的硬面包 绷带 酒精 药物和电池\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two weeks' worth of hardtack, bandages, alcohol, meds, batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.99,0:38:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你们一起去 但我在跨年夜被友军误伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd come with you, but I caught some friendly fire on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.49,0:38:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定是友军吗  - 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You sure it was friendly? - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.16,0:39:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在巡逻队经过之前 你们只有十分钟 快走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got ten minutes before a patrol comes by. Let's get you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.07,0:40:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(乔尔米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.19,0:42:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 字母F\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so...F.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.07,0:43:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,字母F 佛...佛利伍麦克乐团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F. Fleetwood Mac. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.91,0:43:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不对 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nope. - What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.29,0:43:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫不对 这是我的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean, "no"? It's my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的看法是错的 因为弗兰克扎帕真的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, your opinion is wrong because Frank Zappa exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.00,0:43:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 字母G\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.21,0:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绿日乐队 - 不 你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Green Day. - No, you're wrong. It's Guns N' Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.64,0:43:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奥兹奥斯朋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ozzy Osbourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.14,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 分数加倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice! Double points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,L M N O P\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, L-M-N-O, P.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.94,0:43:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要让我猜完所有字母吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you seriously gonna make me do the entire alphabet?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.98,0:43:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我很灵活的 让我想想 换个新话题...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have to. I'm incredibly flexible. Lemme see, new topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沉默也行 - 有了 你杀的第一个人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or silence. - Got one. First person you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.24,0:43:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对 有趣的童年故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, fun stories of childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.20,0:43:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个人死得太离谱 但我可以跟你说说第二个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, the first one's too fucked up, but I can tell you the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.75,0:43:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我和乔尔来杰克逊之前的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a little before Joel and I got to Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.25,0:44:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在堪萨斯城 他被一个没比我大几岁的孩子突袭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Kansas City, he got jumped by this kid, maybe just a couple years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.84,0:44:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我从后面接近他 举起枪 然后...就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I came up behind him, raised my gun and, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.81,0:44:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思 杀人的是我 你却替我难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interesting. I shoot a guy, and you feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.94,0:44:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just loyal like that.
